# Checkout Workflow Implementation Report — Phase 13.7

## Files Modified

| File | Changes |
|------|---------|
| `src/JLek.POS.Web/Components/Cashier/PaymentDialog/PaymentDialog.razor` | Enhanced with Cash amount input, change calculation, method selection (Cash/PromptPay/Card), validation (amount ≥ total), ARIA roles |
| `src/JLek.POS.Web/Components/Cashier/ReceiptPreview/ReceiptPreview.razor` | Enhanced with 3 action buttons (Print & Close Table, Close Table Only, Skip), formatted prices, ARIA roles |

## PaymentDialog Features

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| **Method selection** | 3 methods: Cash, PromptPay, Card with `role="radiogroup"` and `aria-pressed` |
| **Cash amount input** | Auto-filled with total, validation requires amount ≥ total |
| **Change calculation** | Real-time: `Math.Max(0, amountReceived - total)` |
| **Validation** | Inline error when amount < total, Pay button disabled |
| **Processing state** | Spinner + disabled inputs during API call |
| **Keyboard** | Escape to cancel |
| **ARIA** | `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal="true"`, `aria-label="Payment"`, `role="alert"` for errors |

## ReceiptDialog Features

| Feature | Detail |
|---------|--------|
| **Receipt display** | Store name, order ID, items with qty × price + line total |
| **Formatted prices** | ฿XX.XX format throughout |
| **Print & Close Table** | One-click: calls OnPrint then OnCloseTable |
| **Close Table Only** | Releases table without printing |
| **Skip** | Keeps table occupied |
| **ARIA** | `role="dialog"`, `aria-modal="true"`, `aria-label="Receipt"` |

## Complete Cashier Workflow

```text
TableGrid → OrderPanel → MenuModal → Confirm → PaymentDialog
                                                        │
                                                        ├── POST /payments
                                                        │
                                                        ▼
                                                   ReceiptDialog
                                                        │
                                                        ├── Print → POST /receipts/customer
                                                        ├── Close → POST /tables/{id}/release
                                                        └── Skip → return to grid
```

## API Sequence for Complete Checkout

| Step | API | Component |
|------|-----|-----------|
| 1 | `POST /orders/{id}/confirm` | OrderPanel |
| 2 | `POST /payments` | PaymentDialog |
| 3 | `POST /receipts/customer` | ReceiptDialog (optional) |
| 4 | `POST /tables/{id}/release` | ReceiptDialog / OrderPanel |

